
To install Nightlong PPC module copy all the files to the Nightlong directory on your HD.



There are 2 different executables:

NightlongPPC-big (full screen movies. Appropriate for fast PPC setups)

NightlongPPC-small (half-size movies.  For slower PPC setups)



Please register your copy of Nightlong.



